{"tid":621290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男當兵入伍不害怕　在軍營裡遇到真愛","createTime":"2018-04-08T08:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T08:17:41.000Z","uid":72009,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"65c2507598e8b23de5791937c980e86ab22b36af","tid":621290,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T08:00:31.000Z","msg":"泰國每年4月舉行徵兵抽籤，年滿21歲役男要抽籤決定當兵與否，抽中紅籤就是要服役，抽中黑籤則免役，有些人抽中紅籤後當場崩潰，也有人抽到紅籤後，在軍中找到真愛。<br />\n<br />\n據《khaosod》報導，近來當兵話題在網路上引發熱議，像是日前有僧侶跟美妝男，抽到紅籤後當場崩潰，不過也有網友軍中照，照片中兩名身穿軍綠色衣服的男子，在床上依偎在一起甜蜜自拍，並且說「感謝紅籤」，讓網友紛紛祝福「這一定是真愛」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180408/640_cae1d482372bc5eb5e5b3250b28010b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180408%2F640_cae1d482372bc5eb5e5b3250b28010b3.jpg&h=760c883e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85306c4f69d5727411f8e60e775e841f0eb71f67","tid":621290,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T08:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f290d0019040af62479eefee3a12fc0227ff3316","tid":621290,"uid":76879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T08:16:52.000Z","msg":"當兵操到咁大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n兩個晚晚互插變雙花紅棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89748710852104fd18353b3f9b0dd0bac1d4729","tid":621290,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T08:17:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/08/161740_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F08%2F161740_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=c845d913&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}